.TH HMAC256 1 "April 2026" "hmac256 (Libgcrypt) 1.10.3" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hmac256 \- compute HMAC-SHA256 digests with libgcrypt
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hmac256
[\fB\-\-binary\fR] [\fB\-\-stdkey\fR|\fIkey\fR] [\fIfile\fR ...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBhmac256\fR computes HMAC-SHA256 digests for one or more files or for
standard input.
.TP
\fB\-\-binary\fR
Write the raw 32-byte digest instead of the hexadecimal text form.
.TP
\fB\-\-stdkey\fR
Use the historical libgcrypt built-in test key.
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
Print version information and exit.
.TP
\fB\-\-help\fR
Display usage information and exit.
